{"_id":"2fdc5176-033e-404d-9094-569d705ad34b","type":"skill","name":"Athletics","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/athletics.svg","system":{"skill_id":"athletics","domain":"Physical","rank":1,"stat":"strength","description":"The Athletics skill is used in climbing, swimming, running, and jumping. Moving heavy objects, breaking down doors, and tossing your dwarven companion into a group of enemies all use your athletics skill. It often overlaps with Acrobatics; Athletics is used when strength and endurance matter more."}}
